-- By default this file is used by `persistFileWith` in Model.hs (which is imported by Foundation.hs)
-- Syntax for this file here: https://github.com/yesodweb/persistent/blob/master/docs/Persistent-entity-syntax.md

User
    ident Text
    password Text Maybe
    nick Text
    elo Int default=1100
    UniqueNick nick
    UniqueUser ident
    deriving Typeable Show

Email
    email Text
    userId UserId Maybe
    verkey Text Maybe
    UniqueEmail email

Game
    player UserId
    opponent UserId
    history Text
    gameStatus GameStatus  
    deriving Show

AiGame
    player UserId
    history Text
    diff AIDiff
    gameStatus GameStatus
    deriving Show
